{"tid":784702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一件返工遇到既on9客","createTime":"2018-08-18T15:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T02:23:32.000Z","uid":202184,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8292a4674fbe13869e94601b8e28e017833612","tid":784702,"uid":202184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n我做某超市暑期工收銀，有個阿婆買十樣野，九樣野係乾貨，最尾個樣係舊大西瓜(咁因為啲阿姨教我見到人地買西瓜免費比個膠袋佢)，我問個阿婆你需唔需要膠袋，佢話要，咁我同佢講要收五毫子（問題係你最尾先拎舊西瓜出泥我鬼睇到咩）然後佢為左個五毫子鬧我，仲話你唔識啊後生仔，我泥教你濕貨同生果都可以有免費袋！你唔識啊！我都費時同佢嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一次有個男人為左免費拎五毫子膠袋同個收銀阿姨嘈，仲問候人地母親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69a4672297a3b204d247498fd8ec71d6b24b260","tid":784702,"uid":177598,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cba05640980d1e3973ea7137b2311b8da6c1b930","tid":784702,"uid":202184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e69a4672297a3b204d247498fd8ec71d6b24b260","tid":784702,"uid":177598,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"同意啊 真係好cheap 為左個五毫子出賣自己<br />\n咁你係個到做有啲咩見聞分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d690a683a4364c417a4b0933a4b6f31182cc4a0","tid":784702,"uid":177598,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fffd2678e9423796b420061e83e6d0369de3e51a","tid":784702,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e69a4672297a3b204d247498fd8ec71d6b24b260","tid":784702,"uid":177598,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:20:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"全部香港人都cheap過大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f35a1d294bcbb45e3e24829eaf0bb029e83726