ji\" /> <br />\n客人永遠是對得的 員工永遠是錯的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06aefc7abf295987f66f0204eb5ca1cbd00cd3c0","tid":784702,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T17:26:19.000Z","msg":"以前中學返過暑期工做過收銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我找完錢俾個女人就另轉第拎佢要嘅嘢俾佢<br />\n咁我返到去counter見到有張50蚊係枱面以為佢拎漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我咪再遞俾佢 跟住佢問左我一句而家算點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我完全唔知咩事 就話俾返50蚊佢<br />\n然後佢就話要搵經理 再投訴我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母原來條臭西係想增值 增值你就講啦 放張50蚊係枱我撚知你想增值咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩而家大個左識搵啲人工高啲又hea嘅pt 因為香港好多客都對人好撚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25390d437c21695b05d1cbf736db7c3cb26c223","tid":784702,"uid":202184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc0cdc22e8e4b7ff5c28ea77fd691859670419ed","tid":784702,"uid":346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無呢隻藥<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無賣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解無賣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無賣咪無賣囉 有得解架咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚串嘅你 叫你經理出黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無賣就無賣架啦 千鳩幾隻藥要賣齊咩<br />\n<br />\n然後佢問隔離收緊銀個同事經理係邊話要投訴<br />\n個同事笑而不語指住我 佢就無癮咁走左"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T17:27:55.000Z","msg":"好正 諗到佢個樣會係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢7左<br />\n屌啲野無賣味無賣 樣樣野都投訴 投訴完係味會開心啲 安樂啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}